function haserror (value) {
if ((parseInt(value) < 100 && parseInt(value) > 49) || (parseInt(value) == 0))
{
return false;
}
else
{
alert("Enter a value between 50 - 99 or 0 (zero).");
return true
}
} //check
function setColor(e, testvalue, MaxValue) {
if (!isPocket()) { // Pocket DOM does not have a style property
if (testvalue > MaxValue)
e.style.color = '#FF0000' // Make it red
else
e.style.color = '#000000'; // Make it black
}
}
function setStyle(testvalue, MaxValue) {
var strValue = testvalue;
// if (isNaN(testvalue))
// strValue = "";
// else
if (testvalue > MaxValue)
strValue = "("+strValue+")"; // Value is too high
return strValue;
}
function FloatingPoint(ss) {
var r, re;
re = /,/g; //Create regular expression pattern.
r = ss.replace(re, '.'); //Replace ',' with '.'.
return (r);
}
function SubmitTheForm(document, theform, numRows, list) {
list.value = "";
if (numRows != null) {
for (var i=1; i<=numRows; i++) {
if (document.forms[i].ProblemID.value == "")
{ list.value += "0,0,0,0,0,"; }
else {
list.value += "" + document.forms[i].Efficacy1.value;
list.value += "," + document.forms[i].Efficacy2.value;
list.value += "," + document.forms[i].Efficacy3.value;
list.value += "," + document.forms[i].Efficacy4.value;
list.value += "," + document.forms[i].Efficacy5.value;
list.value += ",";
}
}
}
// theform.action="EfficacyResult.asp";
theform.submit();
// return true;
}
function fctRateEfficacyTarget ( MaxRatePerApplication_par,
a_displacement_par,
b_slope_par,
EfficacyTarget,
CultivarCorrection_par,
WeedGSCorrection_par,
TempCorrection_par,
WeedWaterStressCorrection_par) {
var result = Math.pow(10.000,
( ( ( - 0.5 * Math.log (( (CultivarCorrection_par==null?1:CultivarCorrection_par)
* 100 - 100 + EfficacyTarget) / (100 - EfficacyTarget))
- a_displacement_par
)
/ b_slope_par
)
+ custLog (
(WeedGSCorrection_par==null?1:WeedGSCorrection_par)
* (TempCorrection_par==null?1:TempCorrection_par)
* (WeedWaterStressCorrection_par==null?1:WeedWaterStressCorrection_par),
10
)
)
);
return result;
}function custLog(x,base) { // Created 1997 by Brian Risk. http://members.aol.com/brianrisk
return (Math.log(x))/(Math.log(base));
}function RoundToDecimal(dosage, normalDosage) {
var dec = 0;
var s = "";
if (normalDosage < 0.2)
{ dec = 3; }
else
if ((normalDosage >= 0.2) && (normalDosage < 2))
{ dec = 2; }
else
if((normalDosage >= 2) && (normalDosage < 20))
{ dec = 1; }
var val = Math.round(dosage*Math.pow(10,dec))/(Math.pow(10,dec));
return val;
}
